<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Hello <%= @contact.name %>,</h1>

  <p>We are contacting you regarding a booking request for a date at <strong><%= @venue.name %></strong>.</p>

  <h2>Request details:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Date:</strong> <%= l(@booking.gig.date, format: :long) %></li>
    <li><strong>Time:</strong> <%= l(@booking.gig.time, format: :time) %></li>
    <li><strong>Duration:</strong> <%= @booking.gig.duration %></li>
    <li><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @booking.gig.description %></li>
    <li><strong>Budget:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@booking.gig.price, unit: "â‚¬") %></li>
  </ul>

  <p>Can you confirm the availability of your venue for this date?</p>

  <p>We remain at your disposal for any questions.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br>
  The booking team</p>
</body>
</html>
